Hardware Communication Summary
========================================
- Raspberry Pi 3B+ runs the main ADAS software using Python.
- Pi Camera Rev 1.3 connects through CSI interface.
- Raspberry Pi communicates with NodeMCU ESP8266 through USB serial communication.
- Serial device used:
/dev/ttyUSB0

- NodeMCU controls:
  * Green LED (SAFE)
  * Yellow LED (WARNING)
  * Red LED (DANGER)
  * Active buzzer

- HC-SR04 ultrasonic sensor measures obstacle distance.

- LEDs are connected through 260 Ohm resistors.

- Raspberry Pi powered through:
Micro USB cable connected to wall adapter.

- Communication protocol:
UART Serial Communication using PySerial.

